{"type": "article", "id": 5413, "title": "Madera 实木挂钟", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-21T07:27:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233842Jj4SRLgWThXPnv7t.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tOTONO 设计工作室日前发布了最新作品，是一款名为「Madera」的实木挂钟。设计团队在制作过程中遵循严格的极简主义，赋予这款挂钟清晰的几何形状与新鲜明丽的色彩，温暖和自然的胡桃木材质使得 Madera 适宜于挂在符合当代审美的家居环境，用户只需选择自己心仪的时针与分针的配色即可。Madera 将于本周亮相德国科隆的 Designers Tower 。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233841HybKfvQLiPoUVMNm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3390625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052338410ISb7GpTzsgd418B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.696875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233842VMhCQdznZ81vgbYi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}